## .NET / ASP.NET Core .gitignore
## Isključuje build artefakte, binarne fajlove i runtime podatke

# ── Build output ──────────────────────────────────────────
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/

# ── NuGet packages ────────────────────────────────────────
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
**/packages/
!**/packages/build/
.nuget/
nuget.config.user

# ── Visual Studio / Rider artefakti ───────────────────────
.vs/
.idea/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.userprefs

# ── Publish output ────────────────────────────────────────
[Pp]ublish/
[Rr]elease/
[Dd]ebug/

# ── .NET runtime ──────────────────────────────────────────
*.dll
*.exe
*.pdb
*.mdb
*.ilk
*.map
*.exp
*.lib
*.log

# ── Testovi – rezultati i pokrivenost ─────────────────────
TestResults/
coverage/
*.trx
*.coverage
*.coveragexml

# ── Secrets i environment ─────────────────────────────────
appsettings.Development.json
*.env
*.env.local
secrets.json

# ── OS artefakti ──────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
